{"tid":625684,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖]17-18 LIHKG香港女神總會盃四強首回合投選專區 #文詠珊 苟芸慧 李佳芯 朱千雪","createTime":"2018-04-11T15:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T14:23:57.000Z","uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3a846aedb7d0abd7035f9928971c6623a9738c00","tid":625684,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T15:59:33.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:00am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n(冠)文詠珊vs苟芸慧(超)<br />\n(超)李佳芯vs朱千雪(超)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5785eabfb94bb5e1b5b9b4fd93671ba0547c8ac1","tid":625684,"uid":92376,"like":127,"dislike":73,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T16:00:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-18 LIHKG香港女神總會盃四強首回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">*括號內數字為聯賽排名(非聯賽者則以非聯表示)</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-4-12 12am-10pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/sym9mKC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fsym9mKC.png&h=7fc067ad&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ofBNKQi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FofBNKQi.png&h=0e577f1c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(冠1)文詠珊vs苟芸慧(超3)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合盃賽設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"84649d512793e2ed2aa1ab80f5fb1f53208d2097","tid":625684,"uid":92376,"like":117,"dislike":101,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-4-12 12:02am-10:02pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Dnsh6ug.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDnsh6ug.png&h=fe8d1f0e&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/CjPcqWB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FCjPcqWB.png&h=76808bda&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(超2)李佳芯vs朱千雪(超1)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">盃賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">兩回合盃賽設作客十進一優惠，作客女神每得十分可再獲一分。額外分數會獨立計算，如總比分賽和將會按照雙方額外分數多寡以決定勝負。若依然賽和則會每次加時十分鐘，直至分出勝負為止，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"ecce6224d1ad15a515f0418f273dd8354a795baa","tid":625684,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"題外話,我尋晚臨急臨忙先醒起今晚係四強首回合<br />\n差啲就唔記得開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae6d81e41a3be1cbba491bdbeab7182fe1d133c","tid":625684,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"次回合 4月18日<br />\n決賽 4月29日"},{"pid":"422b1f4573312d3fec159791d62a5fdf502c480e","tid":62568